reviewText: This is an amazing study for new believers and for old dogs who need a refresher :)

Our married couples group is almost finished with the 6 part series and it has brought challenges and growth to each of our members. you can hardly go wrong with Andy Stanley and Jeff Henderson  is a great compliment to his teaching. Seriously...this is good stuff even for mature Christians.

We used this DVD for our Life Group study and thoroughly enjoyed the message, presentation and Bible-based application for daily living.  If we could intentionally put each of these topics into action it would likely have a profound impact on the world.  Highly recommend!
